板蓝根颗粒出口海外脱销，可它治不了新冠肺炎。
Banlangen granule exports overseas to sell out, but it can not cure the new crown pneumonia.
金淼。
Miao Jin.
界面新闻                      。
Interface news.
界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
记者 |金淼编辑 |许悦“ 每逢疫情，板蓝根都要被抢购。
At the time of the outbreak, Ms Chen was snapped up.
”随着新冠疫情在全球范围内的蔓延，中国的治疗经验也不断被推广出海。
As the new crown epidemic spreads around the world, China's treatment experience is increasingly being rolled out to sea.
3月17日，国务院联防联控机制召开的新闻发布会上，科技部生物中心主任张新民就表示，法匹拉韦、恢复期血浆、中药等重点药物已向发生疫情的相关国家提供。
Zhang Xinmin, director of the Center for Biology of the Ministry of Science and Technology, said at a press conference held on March 17 by the Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council.
但是未详细透露具体提供的中药品种。
But did not disclose the specific Chinese medicine variety.
中药疗法在新冠治疗中，受到追捧。
Traditional Chinese medicine therapy is very popular in the new crown therapy.
3月10日，国家卫健委、国家中医管理局印发的《新型冠状病毒肺炎诊疗方案（试行第七版）》中，莲花清瘟、藿香正气、金花清感颗粒、安宫牛黄丸等中成药继续在列。
On March 10, the Chinese medicine patent medicine such as lotus rinderpest, patchouli qi, Jinhua Qingseng granules and Angong Niuhuangwan continue to be included in the Diagnosis and Treatment Programme for Coronavirus Pneumonia (Trial Edition 7).
与此同时，海外的中药需求也大幅增加。
At the same time, overseas Chinese medicine demand also increased significantly.
路透社3月10日报道表示，纽约和旧金山两大城市的中草药商铺出现供货紧张，一位中医在采访中表示，其诊所对中草药需求激增，金银花和板蓝根冲剂成为畅销品，价格正迅速上涨。
A Chinese medicine practitioner said in an interview with Chinese herbal medicine shops in New York and San Francisco that demand for Chinese herbs has surged and Honeysuckle and Banlangen granules are big sellers and prices are rising rapidly.
据《上海证券报》报道，以岭药业的莲花清瘟和聚协昌的金花清感两款中药，已随中国医疗专家驰援意大利、伊拉克等国家。
According to the Shanghai Securities Journal, two traditional Chinese medicines, lotus rinderpest from Lingnan Pharmaceutical Company and Ching-seng Jinhua Qingseng, have been sent to Italy and Iraq with Chinese medical experts.
随着中药出海升温，有投资者开始向上市公司询问板蓝根、金银花等中药材出口情况。
With Chinese medicine warming up, investors began to ask listed companies Banlangen, honeysuckle and other Chinese medicinal materials exports.
3月13日，华润三九在投资者关系互动平台上表示，公司海外业务在公司总体业务中占比极小，板蓝根有少量出口业务（近期部分出口用于捐赠）。
On March 13, China Resources 39 said on the Investor Relations Interactive Platform that the company's overseas operations accounted for a very small percentage of the company's overall business, and that Banlangen had a small export business (some of its recent exports were for donations).
随着国内新冠肺炎疫情得到有效控制，海外国家疫情形势日益严峻，公司已在研究中药配方颗粒等品种拓展海外市场的机会。
With the outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia under effective control, overseas countries increasingly serious epidemic situation, the company has been studying Chinese medicine formula granules and other varieties to expand overseas market opportunities.
但实际上，1月21日国家卫健委官方微博健康中国就已经对板蓝根用于新冠肺炎预防的说法进行辟谣，和平里医院呼吸科主任医师张骅表示，板蓝根适用于治疗风热感冒、病毒性感冒等热性疾病的治疗，有一定的抗病毒效果，但是对冠状病毒是不可能有效的。
But in fact, on January 21, the official Weibo Health National Health Commission China has refuted the notion that Banlangen is used in the prevention of new crown pneumonia, and Zhang Hua, director of respiratory department at Pei Li Hospital, said Banlangen is suitable for the treatment of hot diseases such as wind-heat cold and viral cold.
板蓝根在2003年非典疫情暴发期间，名声大噪，作为疫情概念品种，每当疫情出现，便会引发抢购。
Banlangen became famous during the SARS outbreak in 2003, and as a concept, every time an outbreak occurs, it triggers a panic buying.
界面新闻记者在国家药品监督管理局网站检索板蓝根药品相关情况，显示共有1251项纪录。
Interface journalists searched the website of the State Administration of Pharmacy for information on Banlangen drugs, showing a total of 1,251 records.
医药魔方此前报道，2017年国内板蓝根颗粒生产企业有726家，此外还有糖浆剂、软胶囊、泡腾片、咀嚼片、分散片等各种剂型。
Medical Rubik's cube previously reported that in 2017 there were 726 domestic Panlangen granule production enterprises, in addition to sugar slurry, soft capsules, bubble Tablets, chewable tablets, dispersible tablets and other preparations.
但板蓝根颗粒的原料板蓝根饮片一直以来是不合格饮片的重灾区，2017年2月，原国家食药监总局发布的《总局关于54批次中药饮片不合格的通告(2017年第21号)》显示，在54批不合格的中药饮片中，板蓝根不合格数为28批次，占一半以上。
However, the raw material of Banlangen granules, Banlangen Foods, has been a serious disaster area for substandard slices. In February 2017, the General Administration of Food and Drug Administration issued the "Notice of the General Administration of Chinese Medicine No.21 of 2017" on the unqualified 54 batches of Chinese herbal medicine tablets, accounting for more than half.
在2018年3月，国家药典委员会发布《关于板蓝根颗粒质量标准拟增修订的公示》，在板蓝根颗粒的制法、鉴别等方面进行了修订，并增加了含量测定项。
In March 2018, the National Pharmacopoeia Commission published the Notice on Proposed Additions and Amendments to the Quality Standards for Banlangen Granules, which was revised in the preparation, identification and content determination of Banlangen granules.
图片来源：丁香园虽然修订板蓝根颗粒标准，推动了板蓝根颗粒产品质量的提升，但是同时其也带来了板蓝根颗粒产品新一轮的涨价。
Source: Although Lilac Garden revised the standard of the granule, promoted the quality of the products, but it also brought a new round of price increase.
但关于板蓝根的疗效之争，从非典到今天一直都没有落下。
But the battle over the efficacy of Banlangen has not been left behind since SARS.
